      <section eId="sec_CCP-1202">
        <num>CCP 1202</num>
        <heading>1202. Â Form of citation</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-1202__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The date of issuance;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-1202__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The title of the cause;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-1202__subsec_3">
          <num>(3)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The name of the person to whom it is addressed;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-1202__subsec_4">
          <num>(4)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The title and location of the court issuing it; and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-1202__subsec_5">
          <num>(5)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A statement that the person cited must either comply with the demand contained in the petition or make an appearance, either by filing a pleading or otherwise, in the court issuing the citation within the delay provided in Article 1001 under penalty of default.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=111148</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
